  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.32,
      505.69,
      534.05,
      543.07
    ],
    "text": "Fairly heavy falls about 75 mm are likely at some places in Western, Sabaragamuwa, Central and North-western provinces and in Galle and Matara districts.",
